# CODEOWNERS — "red-lane" routing.
#
# Only high-risk paths are listed here on purpose. Everything NOT listed has no
# code owner and flows through normal reviewer assignment. Listing a path here
# means: a code owner must review before merge (once branch protection has
# "Require review from Code Owners" enabled — see the AI code-review playbook).
#
# Owners below are a safe default (@abuaboud). Replace/extend with a security
# team and per-area co-owners as the team grows — GitHub auto-requests every
# listed owner, so keep entries tight to avoid review spam.

